{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a vibrant scene featuring the San Francisco-Oakland Bay Bridge as the prominent focal point. The bridge stretches across a calm, grey-blue bay under a bright blue sky dotted with fluffy white clouds. In the foreground, a wooden pier with metal railings runs horizontally across the bottom of the frame. A person wearing a red jacket is visible on the pier, adding a touch of scale and human presence. Beyond the pier, several boats and ships are scattered across the water. A low, dark-colored building is situated near the bridge's eastern span, and a white building can be seen in the distance. The lighting is strong and sunny, creating clear visibility and highlighting the bridge's structure.",
